{"ID":"20260609125853-ji7laj2","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125853-ji7laj2","title":"2020年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609130009"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125906-tnvvs66","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125906-tnvvs66","updated":"20260609125906"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①让群众早日摆脱贫困，是中阳县的政治责任和使命担当。②中阳县采用鼓励贫困户加入合作社或龙头企业等四种模式，建立贫困户利益联结机制。③"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"通过"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贷款发放，贫困户获得用于创收的生产资金。④"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"通过"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"产业扶贫，保障贫困户每年有稳定的收益。⑤中阳县还积极探索农村集体经济破零增收，借助整合资源、盘活资产、服务企业、购买服务等四种措施，确保贫困村集体收入全部达到五万元以上。⑥"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"通过"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"全力奋战，中阳县脱贫攻坚取得了明显成效。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125853-umul141","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125853-umul141","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-vm6604m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-vm6604m","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"23．下列说法正确的一项是(   )"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-9l47475","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-9l47475","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．①②两句中的“中阳县”都可以改为“该县”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-g6in0bx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-g6in0bx","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．②⑤两句中加点的两个“等”字，用法一样。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-h27nnot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-h27nnot","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．文中三个“通过”，唯有一个可被换为“经过”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-lkd95bl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-lkd95bl","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．将⑥置于①②两句之间，文段会变得更连贯。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125917-n1qjjim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125917-n1qjjim","updated":"20260609125917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"24．文段中③④两句结构不同，请在③中添加一个词，使之在保持原意的基础上与④结构一致，将修改后的句子写在答题纸上。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125853-3uaqw39","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125853-3uaqw39","updated":"20260609125929"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125853-k8yvfzb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125853-k8yvfzb","updated":"20260609125929"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"23．C    24．通过贷款发放，保障/保证/确保/让/使/使得贫困户获得用于创收的生产资金。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125853-ud23dpu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125853-ud23dpu","updated":"20260609130009"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-1qdoibt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-1qdoibt","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"23．本题考查综合语言表达能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-e93wo6v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-e93wo6v","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A项，①句中的“中阳县”不能改成“该县”。如前面已经提到这个县的名字，则下句再提到这个县就可以用“该县”，而①句是首次提到县的名字，必须使用全称“中阳县”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-drkatyb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-drkatyb","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B项，②句中的“等”是表示列举未尽的省略；⑤句中的“等”是表示列举已尽的收束。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-safqxrv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-safqxrv","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C项，⑥“通过全力奋战”的“通过”可以换成“经过”，而③④中的“通过”都不能换成“经过”，否则搭配不当。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-ngn3oc2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-ngn3oc2","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D项，⑥句是说的“结果”，而①句是目标，②句是措施，中间插入⑥不合逻辑。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-8vba9i6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-8vba9i6","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-y9lomyv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-y9lomyv","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"24．本题考查句式的鉴赏能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125940-04e6oih","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125940-04e6oih","updated":"20260609125940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④是“通过产业扶贫，保障贫困户每年有稳定的收益”，格式是“通过……，保障……”。③是“通过贷款发放，贫困户获得用于创收的生产资金”，“贫困户获得用于创收的生产资金”前面需要加一个与“保障”意义类似的动词，可加“保障/保证/确保”或“让/使/使得”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130009-857v2mz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130009-857v2mz","updated":"20260609130009"}}]}